languages.text: "Вам нравится? Я польщена. Не так часто сюда захаживают важные гости, и еще реже они оценивают это место по достоинству".

traits.locale_text: "Вам нравится? Я польщена. Не так часто сюда захаживают важные гости, и еще реже они оценивают это место по достоинству".

languages.text: "You like it? I'm flattered. It's not often that we get important visitors here, and it's even less often that they really appreciate this place."

languages.text: “你喜欢这个名字吗？那我真是受宠若惊。我们这里很少会有大人物来，至于喜欢这里的大人物，就更少了。”
languages.original_text: "You like it? I'm flattered. It's not often that we get important visitors here, and it's even less often that they really appreciate this place."

traits.locale_text: “你喜欢这个名字吗？那我真是受宠若惊。我们这里很少会有大人物来，至于喜欢这里的大人物，就更少了。”

languages.text: «¿Te gusta? Me alegro. No solemos recibir visitantes importantes, y menos aún visitantes que aprecien el mesón».
languages.original_text: "You like it? I'm flattered. It's not often that we get important visitors here, and it's even less often that they really appreciate this place."

traits.locale_text: «¿Te gusta? Me alegro. No solemos recibir visitantes importantes, y menos aún visitantes que aprecien el mesón».

languages.text: 「気に入ってくれたの？嬉しいね。ここに大事なお客さんが来ることは滅多にないし、さらにこの場所を評価してくれる人なんてなおさら珍しいよ」
languages.original_text: "You like it? I'm flattered. It's not often that we get important visitors here, and it's even less often that they really appreciate this place."

traits.locale_text: 「気に入ってくれたの？嬉しいね。ここに大事なお客さんが来ることは滅多にないし、さらにこの場所を評価してくれる人なんてなおさら珍しいよ」

languages.text: "Es gefällt Euch? Wie schmeichelhaft. Wir haben nicht oft wichtige Besucher, und dass es ihnen gefällt, ist noch viel seltener."
languages.original_text: "You like it? I'm flattered. It's not often that we get important visitors here, and it's even less often that they really appreciate this place."

traits.locale_text: "Es gefällt Euch? Wie schmeichelhaft. Wir haben nicht oft wichtige Besucher, und dass es ihnen gefällt, ist noch viel seltener."

languages.text: « Ça vous plaît ? J'en suis flattée. On reçoit rarement des gens importants ici, et c'est encore plus rare qu'ils apprécient l'endroit. »

languages.text: "Beğendiniz mi? Gururum okşandı. Nadiren önemli misafir ağırlarız. Aralarında burayı sahiden beğenenlerinse sayısı bir elin parmaklarını geçmez."
languages.original_text: "You like it? I'm flattered. It's not often that we get important visitors here, and it's even less often that they really appreciate this place."

traits.locale_text: "Beğendiniz mi? Gururum okşandı. Nadiren önemli misafir ağırlayabiliyoruz; ağırladığımız misafirlerimizin de burayı gerçekten beğenmesi daha da nadir oluyor."
